        "text": "1 Chronicles 27:1",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", etc. הם מלאכת ולשׂרי, and as regards the princes of the work of the king. The למּלך וּמקנה רכוּשׁ שׂרי, ",
        "children": []
